%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Here's%20how%20AWS%20is%20helping%20financial%20giants%20like%20JPMorgan%20and%20Bridgewater%20with%20their%20AI%20ambitions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223520%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20smiles%20in%20his%20head%20shot%20wearing%20a%20white%20collared%20shirt%20and%20grey%20suit%20jacket%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c2220bb8b41a9673f95dec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222640%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJohn%20Kain%2C%20head%20of%20financial%20services%20market%20development%20at%20AWS%3Cp%3EAWS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAmazon%20Web%20Services%20provides%20data%20and%20computing%20technology%20to%20other%20companies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20has%20become%20a%20key%20part%20of%20Wall%20Street%20technology%2C%20with%20many%20firms%20relying%20on%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHere's%20how%20it's%20helping%20finance%20firms%20and%20fintechs%20with%20generative%20AI%20efforts.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGenerative%20AI%20has%20upped%20the%20ante%20in%20the%20public%20cloud%20war%20for%20Wall%20Street's%20wallet%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20Web%20Services%2C%20Microsoft%20Azure%2C%20and%20Google%20Cloud%2C%20the%20cloud-computing%20arms%20of%20the%20respective%20Big%20Tech%20companies%2C%20have%20been%20duking%20it%20out%20to%20be%20the%20financial%20industry's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faws-google-cloud-ibm-microsoft-public-cloud-strengths-wall-street-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ego-to%20cloud%20provider%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Strategies%20to%20win%20that%20business%20extended%20beyond%20just%20providing%20technology%20%E2%80%94%20many%20are%20now%20focusing%20on%20helping%20clients%20roll%20out%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20keep%20its%20edge%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-earnings-call-report-amzn-stock-live-updates-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20plans%20to%20deploy%20around%20%24105%20billion%20in%20its%20business%2C%20much%20of%20which%20will%20go%20toward%20AWS%20and%20its%20AI%20efforts.%20For%20a%20look%20at%20how%20that%20money%20may%20touch%20Wall%20Street%2C%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20with%20John%20Kain%2C%20the%20head%20of%20financial%20services%20market%20development%20at%20AWS.%20Kain%2C%20who%20worked%20at%20JPMorgan%20Chase%20and%20Nasdaq%20before%20switching%20industries%2C%20outlined%20the%20future%20direction%20of%20AWS'%20Wall%20Street%20business%20through%20four%20different%20clients%3A%20two%20large%20international%20banks%2C%20a%20hedge%20fund%2C%20and%20a%20fintech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20tasks%20are%20getting%20more%20complex%2C%20things%20are%20becoming%20much%20more%20agentic%20in%20nature%2C%20much%20more%20tailored%20for%20individual%20use%20cases%20to%20get%20real%20price%20performance%20benefits%2C%26quot%3B%20Kain%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20industry's%20AI%20maturity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20the%20work%20behind%20the%20scenes%20has%20been%20around%20cutting%20down%20on%20the%20number%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-openai-ai-dictionary-help-understand-nvidia-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehallucinations%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20common%20issue%20where%20inaccurate%20responses%20are%20presented%20as%20fact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20example%20is%20with%20AWS%20Bedrock%2C%20a%20service%20that%20helps%20customers%20build%20generative%20AI%20applications%20and%20models.%20Last%20year%2C%20AWS%20introduced%20a%20feature%20called%20Bedrock%20Guardrails%20that%20looks%20at%20the%20responses%20coming%20out%20of%20large%20language%20models%2C%20and%20then%20uses%20another%20large%20language%20model%20to%20check%20whether%20that%20answer%20actually%20was%20a%20good%20response.%20In%20some%20cases%2C%20this%20approach%20detected%20about%2075%25%20of%20hallucinations%2C%20Kain%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20AWS%20efforts%2C%20like%20automated%20reasoning%2C%20have%20tried%20to%20use%20mathematical%20proofs%20to%20prove%20that%20the%20information%20from%20generative%20AI%20models%20is%20factually%20correct.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20AWS%20is%20helping%20Wall%20Street%20firms%20use%20generative%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221025bd24-db72-48df-8886-ac3c7e1a42d7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EJPMorgan%20Chase%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAWS%20focus%20area%3A%20Security%20and%20scale%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-tech-chief-lori-beer-leadership-team-ai%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELori%20Beer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20JPMorgan's%20global%20chief%20information%20officer%2C%20took%20the%20stage%20at%20AWS%20re%3AInvent%20in%20December%2C%20she%20charted%20the%20bank's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-public-cloud-computing-strategy-hybrid-tech-edge-costs-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eembrace%20of%20the%20cloud%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20started%20in%202017.%20In%202020%2C%20JPM%20had%20100%20apps%20in%20the%20cloud%2C%20and%20it%20doubled%20that%20number%20the%20following%20year.%20It%20also%20built%20its%20UK%20consumer%20bank%20from%20the%20ground%20up%20on%20AWS.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJPMorgan%20now%20has%20thousands%20of%20applications%20running%20on%20AWS%20that%20fully%20take%20advantage%20of%20generative%20AI%20technologies%2C%20Kain%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22575%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lori%20Beer%20JPMorgan%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c238f5b8b41a9673f96358%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22431%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELori%20Beer%2C%20CIO%20at%20JPMorgan%20Chase.%3Cp%3EJPMorgan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJPMorgan's%20internal%20data%20and%20AI%20platform%20relies%20on%20AWS%20SageMaker%2C%20a%20tool%20for%20creating%20and%20training%20machine-learning%20models%2C%20with%20more%20than%205%2C000%20employees%20using%20the%20cloud-based%20tool%20every%20month%2C%20Beer%20said.%20The%20bank%20has%20simplified%20the%20process%20of%20developing%20new%20models%2C%20from%20experimentation%20to%20deploying%20them%20live%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20platform%20is%20empowering%20us%20to%20build%20the%20next%20wave%20of%20AI%20applications%20at%20the%20firm%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecurity%2C%20governance%2C%20and%20compliance%20measures%20in%20the%20cloud%20were%20key%20to%20JPMorgan's%20uptake%2C%20according%20to%20Kain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJPMorgan%2C%20which%20processes%20%2410%20trillion%20in%20payments%20daily%20and%20counts%2082%20million%20customers%20in%20the%20US%2C%20is%20considered%20the%20world's%20most%20systemically%20important%20bank%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fsb.org%2F2024%2F11%2F2024-list-of-global-systemically-important-banks-g-sibs%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Financial%2520Stability%2520Board%2520(FSB%2Cbanks%2520(G%252DSIBs).%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Financial%20Stability%20Board%2C%20which%20identifies%20global%20systemically%20important%20financial%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOrganizations%20like%20JPMorgan%2C%20they%20have%20a%20unique%20scale%20and%20complexity%20that%20comes%20with%20being%20a%20globally%20regulated%20organization%20in%20multiple%20lines%20of%20business%20and%20we%20get%20to%20learn%20alongside%20of%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Kain%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20bank's%20business%20compliance%20and%20security%20perspective%20helped%20drive%20AWS'%20roadmap%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d603ed40-e17b-42c9-bd4c-02209c9d2fa9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBridgewater%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAWS%20focus%20area%3A%20coordinating%20specialized%20models%20for%20investment%20research%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20Bridgewater%20pulled%20together%20a%20group%20of%20investors%2C%20data%20scientists%2C%20and%20technologists%20to%20rethink%20how%20the%20hedge%20fund%20understood%20markets%20and%20economies%20with%20AI%20and%20machine%20learning%20first.%20Thus%2C%20AIA%20Labs%20was%20born.%20Short%20for%20artificial%20investment%20associate%2C%20the%20division%20within%20the%20investment%20firm%20sought%20to%20recreate%20%26quot%3Beverything%20that%20we%20do%20via%20machine-learning%20techniques%2C%26quot%3B%20Bridgewater's%20co-chief%20investment%20officer%20Greg%20Jensen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbridgewater-building-ai-fund-machine-learning-greg-jensen-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20told%20BI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227903%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22headshot%20of%20Bridgewater%20Associates%20co-CIO%20Greg%20Jensen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6362c37eff27460018ed4e35%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224929%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBridgewater%20Associates%20co-CIO%20Greg%20Jensen.%3Cp%3EBridgewater%20Associates%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20started%20on%20a%20notepad%2C%20graduated%20to%20Excel%2C%20and%20is%20now%20running%20on%20EKS%20and%20various%20other%20AWS%20services%2C%26quot%3B%20AIA%20Labs%20CTO%20Aaron%20Linsky%20said%20at%20re%3AInvent%20in%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarly%20on%2C%20the%20capabilities%20on%20the%20generative%20AI%20side%20were%20mostly%20limited%20to%20asking%20a%20straightforward%20question%2C%20getting%20the%20AI%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20write%20code%20to%20exract%20that%20data%20from%20Bridgewater's%20system%2C%20and%20produce%20a%20response%2C%20Kain%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20was%20great%2C%20it%20was%20saving%20hours%20and%20hours%20of%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20and%20made%20it%20so%20investment%20analysts%20didn't%20have%20to%20bug%20developers%20to%20get%20the%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Bridgewater's%20AI%20platform%20can%20take%20a%20complex%20investing%20strategy%20and%20analyze%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20showed%20how%20they%20were%20able%20to%20take%20that%20complex%20investment%20question%2C%20break%20it%20into%20multiple%20steps%2C%20and%20have%20each%20of%20those%20steps%20go%20out%20to%20a%20particular%20agent%2C%26quot%3B%20Kain%20said.%20For%20example%2C%20one%20agent%20may%20check%20how%20interest%20rates%20affect%20overall%20returns%2C%20another%20could%20double-check%20the%20financials%2C%20and%20a%20third%20may%20summarize%20the%20risk%20profile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20found%20today%20that%20limiting%20the%20breadth%20of%20responsibilities%20for%20any%20given%20agent%20is%20really%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20Linsky%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20on%20the%20path%20towards%20full%20agentic%20workflows%2C%26quot%3B%20Linsky%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe're%20definitely%20not%20replacing%20our%20investment%20associates%20with%20the%20capabilities%20right%20now%2C%20but%20it%20is%20helping%20to%20speed%20along%20their%20process.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227bd475dd-0876-4748-9df4-3db5787a7683%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMUFG%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAWS%20focus%20area%3A%20turning%20multiple%20data%20sets%20into%20new%20sales%20ideas%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMitsubishi%20UFJ%20Financial%20Group%2C%20which%20offers%20everything%20from%20investment%20banking%20to%20treasury%20management%20and%20trade%20finance%2C%20is%20using%20generative%20AI%20to%20give%20its%20corporate%20salespeople%20a%20leg%20up.%20An%20AI%20platform%20that%20suggests%20sales%20ideas%20has%20led%20to%20a%2030%25%20conversion%20rate%2C%20Tetsuo%20Horigane%2C%20head%20of%20quant%20innovation%20at%20MUFG%2C%20said%20at%20re%3AInvent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22MUFG%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5c1944adb3c21d6b690e07a7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221368%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMitsubishi%20UFJ%20Financial%20Group%20(MUFG)%20is%20a%20large%20Japanese%20bank.%3Cp%3EKazuhiro%20Nogi%2FAFP%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMUFG%20began%20developing%20generative%20AI%20applications%20in%202023%20after%20launching%20an%20in-house%20AI%2FML%20team%20two%20years%20prior%2C%20Horigane%20said.%20MUFG%20also%20has%20about%202%2C000%20employees%20serving%20roughly%201%20million%20corporate%20clients%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bank's%20salespeople%20typically%20read%20through%20hundreds%20or%20thousands%20of%20pages%20of%20documents%20to%20understand%20a%20given%20client's%20situation%20and%20what%20financial%20product%20is%20most%20relevant%20to%20them.%20But%20now%20the%20AI%20platform%20combines%20multiple%20data%20sets%2C%20like%20the%20client's%20transaction%20history%2C%20previous%20sales%20conversions%20to%20understand%20what%20they're%20in%20the%20market%20for%2C%20their%20financial%20filings%2C%20and%20public%20information%20like%20news%2C%20Kain%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20process%20of%20drafting%20a%20sales%20pitch%2C%20which%20could%20take%20several%20hours%20or%20days%2C%20could%20now%20be%20done%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20minutes%2C%20Horigane%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22483702d1-5958-4dc2-a0f3-1ed14965ac9c%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAWS%20focus%20area%3A%20using%20call%20center%20AI%20to%20influence%20strategy%20and%20experience%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20in%20call%20centers%20is%20nothing%20novel%2C%20but%20for%20Rocket%20Mortgage%2C%20it's%20leading%20executives%20to%20think%20about%20whole%20new%20strategies%20and%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fintech%20integrated%20AWS's%20generative%20AI%20technology%20into%20its%20call%20centers%20to%20lessen%20the%20load%20for%20its%20thousands%20of%20call%20center%20employees%20who%20field%20calls%2C%20emails%2C%20and%20webchats%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20idea%20is%20not%20just%20to%20have%20one%20AI%20assistant%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Ban%20entire%20network%20of%20agents%2C%26quot%3B%20Dan%20Vasquez%2C%20VP%20of%20AI%20strategy%20at%20Rocket%20Mortgage%2C%20said%20at%20re%3AInvent.%20They%20help%20with%20transcribing%2C%20picking%20out%20key%20pieces%20of%20information%20mid-call%2C%20and%20providing%20insights%20and%20data%20about%20the%20call%20after%20the%20fact%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGenerative%20AI%20has%20helped%20save%20some%2040%2C000%20hours%20annually%20for%20call%20center%20employees%20and%20enabled%2070%25%20of%20client%20support%20to%20be%20fully%20self-served%2C%20Vasquez%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20now%2C%20Rocket%20Mortgage%20is%20using%20those%2010%20petabytes%20of%20data%20to%20figure%20out%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20should%20we%20do%20next%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20the%20real%20benefit%2C%20Kain%20said%2C%20for%20the%20fintech%20to%20start%20asking%20big%20questions%20like%20%26quot%3Bwhy%20are%20my%20customers%20calling%20me%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20are%20my%20most%20common%20problems%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20use%20that%20intel%20to%20rethink%20its%20online%20platforms%2C%20streamline%20workflows%2C%20and%20improve%20the%20overall%20customer%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faws-wall-street-jpmorgan-bridgewater-mufg-rocket-mortgage-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740916802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6765ac3f6c531c315b8997bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faws-wall-street-jpmorgan-bridgewater-mufg-rocket-mortgage-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20boosting%20corporate%20sales%20at%20MUFG%20to%20giving%20Bridgewater%20tools