%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20first%20few%20weeks%20were%20filled%20with%20loneliness%2C%20doubt%2C%20and%20insecurity.%20It%20felt%20like%20our%20relationship%20had%20suddenly%20become%20fragile%2C%20vulnerable%20to%20time%20and%20distance.%20I%20worried%20that%20absence%20would%20create%20a%20gap%20in%20our%20connection%20and%20that%20the%20intimacy%20we%20once%20shared%20would%20slowly%20disappear.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20had%20relied%20on%20proximity%20as%20a%20kind%20of%20evidence%20of%20love.%20Without%20the%20constant%20comfort%20of%20being%20his%20physical%20presence%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20spiraling.%20Did%20he%20miss%20me%20as%20much%20as%20I%20missed%20him%3F%20Were%20we%20drifting%20apart%20without%20noticing%3F%20After%20being%20together%20less%20than%20a%20year%2C%20I%20wondered%20if%20our%20foundation%20was%20strong%20enough%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-make-unplanned-long-distance-relationship-work-2020-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esurvive%20the%20distance%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20I%20didn't%20expect%20how%20much%20this%20difficult%20period%20would%20teach%20me%20about%20real%20partnership.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22675fbb27-7477-415b-9cf0-6bbfeb5a4758%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20way%20we%20communicate%20has%20changed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20you%20can't%20rely%20on%20casual%20everyday%20in-person%20exchanges%2C%20communication%20becomes%20an%20intentional%20act.%20Each%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprefer-phone-calls-texting-communication-style-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ephone%20call%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20every%20text%20message%2C%20now%20feels%20deliberate.%20At%20first%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20struggling%20to%20replicate%20the%20easy%20flow%20of%20our%20conversations.%20I%20had%20to%20make%20a%20conscious%20effort%20to%20express%20my%20emotions%20clearly%20rather%20than%20assuming%20he%20could%20intuitively%20understand%20me%20without%20facial%20expressions%20or%20vocal%20inflection.%20Every%20conversation%20now%2C%20outside%20our%20ongoing%20text%20thread%2C%20is%20a%20choice%2C%20and%20both%20of%20us%20have%20to%20make%20that%20choice%20to%20create%20closeness.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe've%20learned%20that%20we%20need%20to%20voice%20our%20thoughts%2C%20worries%2C%20and%20fears%20to%20avoid%20misunderstandings.%20While%20structure%20is%20helpful%20%E2%80%94%20like%20scheduled%20phone%20calls%20and%20check-ins%20%E2%80%94%20we've%20also%20learned%20that%20spontaneity%20matters.%20A%20playful%20text%20or%20an%20unexpected%20message%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20day%20helps%20us%20feel%20more%20connected.%20A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshared-google-calendar-key-successful-marriage-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eshared%20calendar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20helps%20us%20coordinate%20visits%20and%20ensure%20we're%20making%20time%20for%20each%20other%2C%20but%20we've%20realized%20that%20staying%20connected%20is%20about%20more%20than%20just%20logistics.%20It's%20about%20making%20room%20for%20both%20routine%20and%20surprise.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ea56bf1e-8f4e-4816-b0db-18c46ad1845c%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI've%20rethought%20what%20it%20means%20to%20be%20in%20a%20healthy%20relationship%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%20a%20moment%20early%20on%20when%20I%20felt%20a%20wave%20of%20jealousy%2C%20even%20though%20there%20was%20no%20legitimate%20reason%20for%20it.%20Fear%20had%20its%20roots%20in%20being%20out%20of%20sight%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20out%20of%20mind.%20This%20fear%2C%20I%20quickly%20realized%2C%20wasn't%20about%20him%20or%20anything%20he%20was%20doing%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20about%20me.%20The%20distance%20forced%20me%20to%20ask%20myself%2C%20%26quot%3BDo%20I%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsecrets-destroy-trust-relationship-therapist-advice-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etrust%20this%20relationship%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20or%20do%20I%20only%20trust%20it%20when%20I%20can%20see%20it%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20new%20chapter%20has%20been%20an%20invitation%20to%20confront%20my%20insecurities%20within%20our%20relationship.%20Ongoing%20conversations%20have%20been%20crucial%20in%20navigating%20those%20feelings%2C%20and%20his%20commitment%20to%20listening%2C%20validating%2C%20and%20holding%20space%20for%20them%20has%20meant%20so%20much.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20I%20also%20realized%20that%20reassurance%20couldn't%20always%20come%20from%20him%20%E2%80%94%20it%20had%20to%20come%20from%20me.%20I've%20learned%20trust%20isn't%20about%20needing%20daily%20proof%20or%20physical%20presence%3B%20it's%20about%20having%20faith%20in%20the%20foundation%20we've%20already%20built.%20Over%20time%2C%20I've%20come%20to%20understand%20that%20I%20need%20to%20be%20intentional%20and%20grounded%20and%20allow%20myself%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-tell-when-teen-is-uncomfortable-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esit%20with%20discomfort%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20rather%20than%20trying%20to%20avoid%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20experience%20has%20forced%20me%20to%20rethink%20what%20it%20means%20to%20be%20in%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsigns-youre-in-a-healthy-relationship-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehealthy%20relationship%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20I%20used%20to%20think%20it%20meant%20completely%20merging%20with%20someone%20else%2C%20losing%20myself%20in%20the%20process%2C%20and%20centering%20my%20life%20