e%20a%20course%20that%20starts%20with%20data%20science%20and%20AI%20for%20everyone%2C%26quot%3B%20Bachas%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20students%20will%20come%20in%20without%20any%20background%20in%20computing%20%E2%80%94%20they%20may%20not%20even%20know%20coding%2C%20but%20they%20get%20this%20teaser%20as%20a%20starter%20course%20through%20which%20they%20can%20become%20interested%20in%20the%20subject%20matter%20and%20then%20continue%20into%20one%20of%20these%20other%20programs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBachas%20said%20the%20aim%20is%20to%20open%20up%20a%20field%20that%20can%20appear%20daunting%20to%20those%20without%20the%20prerequisite%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20other%20words%2C%20don't%20be%20scared%20about%20the%20field%20of%20computer%20science%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20computer%20science%20class%20for%20all%2C%20and%20then%20a%20data%20science%20class%20for%20all%2C%20an%20artificial%20intelligence%20class%20for%20all%2C%20to%20try%20to%20bring%20students%20slowly%20from%20disciplines%20that%20may%20not%20be%20accustomed%20to%20view%20computing%20as%20friendly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMitsunori%20Ogihara%2C%20a%20professor%20in%20the%20Department%20of%20Computer%20Science%20at%20UM%20who%20helped%20design%20the%20university's%20B.S.%20in%20Data%20Science%20and%20AI%2C%20said%20he%20hopes%20that%20students%20come%20to%20respect%20it%20as%20a%20core%20subject%20of%20sorts%2C%20much%20like%20mathematics.%20With%20greater%20understanding%2C%20Ogihara%20said%2C%20comes%20the%20lessening%20of%20anxiety%20surrounding%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-new-dark-age-risks-regulations-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epotential%20ramifications%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhenever%20there%20is%20this%20new%20development%20that%20occurs%2C%20lay-people's%20reaction%20is%2C%20'Oh%2C%20I'm%20totally%20scared%20of%20this.%20The%20computer%20scientists%20are%20conspiring%20to%20do%20ve