profits%20from%20hedge-fund-style%20trading%20strategies%20that%20require%20greater%20risk%20and%20longer%20holding%20periods%2C%20and%20a%20unit%20dedicated%20to%20such%20strategies%20called%20Prism%20has%20become%20a%20key%20profit%20driver%2C%20the%20people%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesman%20for%20HRT%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%202002%2C%20HRT%20is%20among%20the%20cadre%20of%20private%20trading%20firms%20that%20capitalized%20on%20the%20electronic-trading%20evolution%20in%20the%20late%201990s%20and%202000s%2C%20applying%20algorithms%20and%20state-of-the%20art%20technology%20to%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHRT%20started%20out%20trading%20US%20cash%20equities%20and%20it%20now%20handles%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhudson-river-trading-taps-google-cloud-quant-research-ai-chips-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E10%25%20of%20the%20total%20stock-trading%20volume%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20it%20has%20expanded%20significantly%2C%20trading%20in%20more%20than%20200%20markets%20across%20a%20broad%20array%20of%20asset%20classes%2C%20including%20futures%2C%20fixed-income%2C%20currencies%2C%20options%2C%20and%20crypto.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20expansion%20has%20doubled%20the%20firm's%20size%20over%20the%20last%20four%20years.%20HRT%20now%20has%2014%20offices%20around%20the%20world%2C%20with%20locations%20in%20traditional%20global%20trading%20hubs%20but%20also%20Austin%2C%20Boulder%2C%20Shanghai%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20Dublin.%20Employee%20head%20count%20has%20climbed%20to%201%2C110%20from%20500%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHRT's%20equity%20capital%20base%20has%20grown%2016-fold%20since%202018%2C%20according%20to%20S%26amp%3BP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20in%20a%20rare%20external%20media%20appearance%2C%20HRT%20revealed%20plans%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fhigh-frequency-trader-hudson-river-to-execute-retail-stock-trades-11625047200%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuild%20out%20a%20wholesale%20marketmaking%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20handle%20order%20flow%20from%20brokers%20like%20Fidelity%20or%20Charles%20Schwab%20%E2%80%94%20to%20capitalize%20on%20the%20explosion%20of%20retail%20stock%20trading.%20It%20has%20grown%20that%20operation%20into%20a%204.7%25%20market%20share%20as%20of%20the%20end%20of%20September%2C%20according%20to%20S%26amp%3BP%2C%20though%20it%20is%20still%20far%20behind%20the%20likes%20of%20Citadel%20Securities%20and%20Virtu%20Financial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d31ce00d-94f0-4a17-89e9-fafca16c1367%5C%22%3EBehind%20HRT's%20growth%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EProprietary%20trading%20firms%20have%20become%20dominant%20forces%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifre.com%2Fstory%2F5133835%2Ftrading-firms-ride-prop-market-making-to-new-heights-dctjzljmpn%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewresting%20billions%20in%20market%20share%3C%2Fa%3E%20away%20from%20global%20investment%20banks%20in%20recent%20years.%20Many%20firms%20experienced%20a%20jolt%20to%20their%20businesses%20in%202020%20and%202021%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20which%20saw%20record%20market%20volatility%20and%20a%20substantial%20increase%20in%20retail%20trading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20firms%20grew%2C%20but%20some%20have%20had%20more%20success%20than%20others.%20Analysts%20estimate%20that%20in%202024%20Jane%20Street%2C%20now%20the%20industry%20Goliath%2C%20reaped%20%2420%20billion%20and%20Citadel%20Securities%20around%20%2410%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20financial%20publication%20International%20Financing%20Review.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20long%20lurked%20under%20the%20surface%20as%20secretive%20market%20players%20that%20mint%20billions%20of%20dollars%20in%20the%20shadows.%20Because%20they%20manage%20their%20own%20money%2C%20unlike%20hedge%20funds%20that%20do%20it%20on%20behalf%20of%20outside%20investors%2C%20they%20report%20little%20information%20to%20the%20outside%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20they%20remain%20closely%20guarded%2C%20this%20has%20started%20to%20change%20in%20recent%20years%20as%20their%20size%20and%20ambitions%20have%20ballooned.%20To%20fund%20their%20expansion%2C%20firms%20like%20Jane%20Street%2C%20Citadel%20Securities%2C%20and%20HRT%20have%20tapped%20debt%20capital%20markets%2C%20giving%20creditors%20and%20ratings%20agencies%20a%20slight%20peak%20under%20the%20hood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHRT%20issued%20a%20%242.1%20billion%20term%20loan%20in%20November%2C%20primarily%20to%20refinance%20and%20extend%20existing%20liabilities.%20In%20research%20reports%20related%20to%20the%20debt%20offering%2C%20both%20Moody's%20and%20S%26amp%3BP%20noted%20HRT%20had%20consistently%20had%20strong%20earnings%20across%20a%20more%20diverse%20set%20of%20strategies%20since%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSturdy%20and%20consistent%20trading%20profits%20have%20led%20to%20improvements%20in%20HRT's%20funding%20and%20liquidity%2C%20evidenced%20by%20consistent%20growth%20in%20trading%20capital%2C%20equity%20capital%2C%20and%20related%20improvements%20in%20its%20trading%20capital%2Fdebt%2C%26quot%3B%20Moody's%20wrote%20in%20its%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226c486021-2329-4424-939d-60811cdc8e8a%5C%22%3EProfits%20by%20Prism%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EProp%20trading%20firms%20have%20traditionally%20relied%20on%20automated%20programs%20and%20speed%20to%20mint%20their%20profits%20%E2%80%94%20continuously%20buying%20and%20selling%20securities%20almost%20instantaneously%20and%20collecting%20tiny%20profits%20that%20add%20up%20to%20millions%20of%20dollars%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there's%20a%20finite%20pool%20of%20money%20in%20market%20making%2C%20and%20it's%20fiercely%20fought%20over.%20Prop%20trading%20firms%20have%20increasingly%20dipped%20their%20toes%20into%20strategies%20more%20associated%20with%20hedge%20funds%2C%20where%20potentially%20even%20greater%20profits%2C%20but%20also%20risks%2C%20lie.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo-called%20mid-frequency%20strategies%20can%20happen%20over%