%20rise%2C%20especially%20for%20over%20a%20decade%2C%20that%20sustained%20performance%20suggests%20it's%20doing%20something%20right.%20And%20it%20could%20be%20a%20good%20starting%20point%20to%20filter%20for%20good%20long-term%20investments%20or%20see%20if%20any%20common%20characteristics%20helped%20them%20succeed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmy%20Arnott%2C%20a%20portfolio%20strategist%20at%20Morningstar%2C%20recently%20did%20just%20that%20by%20pulling%20a%20list%20of%20the%20top%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fstock-trading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estocks%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20have%20created%20the%20most%20value%20for%20investors%20over%20the%20past%20decade.%20One%20common%20denominator%20among%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20them%20is%20that%20they%20have%20wide%20economic%20moats%2C%20which%20means%20they%20are%20less%20likely%20to%20face%20competition%20in%20the%20next%2020%20years.%20This%20is%20especially%20important%20for%20companies%20spending%20mega%20dollars%20%E2%80%94%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DH3RRDhEgqcM%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20players%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20in%20hopes%20of%20reaping%20long-term%20benefits%20and%20wider%20market%20share.%20And%20to%20do%20that%2C%20they%20need%20a%20long%20runway%20with%20little%20competion%20to%20reap%20the%20returns%20of%20their%20capital%20expenditure%20for%20many%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20found%20that%20stocks%20able%20to%20create%20a%20lot%20of%20value%20over%20long%20periods%20of%20time%20tend%20to%20continue%20performing%20well%20for%20many%20years%2C%20which%20reinforces%20the%20approach%20of%20Warren%20Buffett%2C%20who%20once%20quipped%20that%20the%20ideal%20holding%20period%20is%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20instance%2C%20Arnott%20measured%20value%20creation%20by%20looking%20at%20the%20biggest%20increases%20in%20market%20cap%20from%202015%20through%202024%2C%20plus%20the%20value%20of%20dividends%20each%20company%20paid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20list%20she%20pulled%20includes%2015%20sector-neutral%20names.%20Unsurprisingly%2C%20Big%20Tech%2C%20and%20more%20specifically%20Nvidia%2C%20tops%20the%20list%20as%20the%20stock%20that%20has%20returned%20the%20most%20value%20to%20shareholders%2C%20with%20more%20than%20%243%20trillion%20in%20value%20created.%20It%20is%20followed%20by%20Apple%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20Amazon%2C%20Alphabet%2C%20Meta%2C%20Tesla%2C%20and%20Broadcom%2C%20all%20of%20which%20created%20more%20than%20%241%20trillion%20in%20shareholder%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20even%20if%20these%20names%20are%20well%20recognized%2C%20it%20doesn't%20mean%20it's%20a%20good%20time%20to%20buy%20shares.%20While%20there's%20a%20mixed%20bag%20of%20reasons%20a%20stock%20can%20fall%20out%20of%20favor%2C%20one%20of%20the%20central%20ones%20is%20simply%20that%20the%20share%20price%20already%20reflects%20the%20strength%20of%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENonetheless%2C%20three%20names%20stand%20out%20for%20being%20rated%20four%20stars%20out%20of%20five%2C%20which%20means%20Morningstar%20considers%20them%20moderately%20undervalued%20or%20trading%20at%20slight%20discounts%20to%20their%20analysts'%20fair-value%20estimates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bb4d9c1e-07ef-4cba-b6f2-fafafb553b58%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E3%20stocks%20that%20are%20still%20discounted%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fmsft-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMicrosoft%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eis%20one%20of%20the%20Big%20Tech%20players%20being%20pulled%20forward%20by%20its%20AI%20innovation%2C%20particularly%20its%20cloud%20computing%20platform%20Azure.%20While%20revenue%20growth%20is%20expected%20to%20slow%20for%20the%20giant%2C%20going%20from%2015.7%25%20in%202024%20to%2013.2%25%20by%202026%2C%20the%20company's%20operating%20margin%20is%20expanding%2C%20from%2044.6%25%20in%202024%20to%2045.1%25%20by%202026%3B%20it's%20a%20sign%20of%20continued%20profitability%20and%20efficient%20capital%20expenditure%2C%20a%20key%20gauge%20of%20successful%20expansion%20amid%20steep%20AI%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20fair%20value%20estimate%2C%20according%20to%20Morningstar%2C%20is%20%24490%20a%20share.%20As%20of%20Friday%2C%20it%20was%20trading%20near%20%24391%20a%20share%2C%20meaning%20it's%20still%20at%20a%20discount.%20Morningstar's%20senior%20analyst%20Dan%20Romanoff's%20conviction%20on%20the%20price%20target%20rides%20on%20expectations%20of%20growing%20profitability%20from%20its%20cloud%20computing%20platform%20Azure%2C%20its%20next-level%20offerings%20in%20Office%20365%20E5%2C%20and%20its%20Power%20Platform%2C%20which%20allows%20companies%20to%20develop%20websites%20and%20apps%20simply.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fgoogl-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlphabet%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20another%20major%20player%20in%20the%20cloud%20computing%20space%20that's%20also%20spending%20big%20bucks%20on%20AI%20development.%20One%20hiccup%20the%20giant%20tech%20firm%20faces%20is%20capacity%20limits%20on%20its%20cloud%20platform%2C%20which%20has%20slowed%20revenue%20growth.%20However%2C%20Malik%20Ahmed%20Khan%2C%20an%20equity%20analyst%20at%20Morningstar%2C%20expects%20capacity%20to%20widen%20which%20will%20pick%20growth%20back%20up.%20Meanwhile%2C%20he%20points%20to%20other%20areas%20of%20Google's%20strength%2C%20including%20revenue%20growth%20from%20its%20AI-driven%20search%20engine%20and%20its%20YouTube%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20the%20search%20engine%20giant's%20revenue%20is%20expected%20to%20slow%2C%20its%20operating%20margin%20is%20expected%20to%20expand%20slightly%20from%2032.1%25%20in%202024%20to%2032.3%25%20by%202025.%20The%20analyst%20increased%20the%20stock's%20fair%20value%20estimate%20from%20%24220%20to%20%24237%