es-first-player-ever-in-cricket-to-7828835%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Uttarakhand%20avalanche%3A%20Army%20recovers%202%20more%20bodies%3B%201%20worker%20still%20missing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740909335000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-avalanche-army-recovers-2-more-bodies-1-worker-still-missing-125030200261_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Uttarakhand%20Chief%20Minister%20Pushkar%20Singh%20Dhami%20said%20this%20morning%20that%20the%20search%20and%20rescue%20operation%20for%20the%20missing%20workers%20is%20ongoing%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Union%20Minister's%20Daughter%20Harassed%20At%20Maharashtra%20Fair%2C%201%20Arrested%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20junior%20minister%20in%20the%20Union%20cabinet%20has%20raised%20questions%20over%20women's%20safety%20in%20Maharashtra%20after%20her%20minor%20daughter%20was%20harassed%20at%20a%20fair%20in%20Jalgaon%20district%2C%20giving%20ammunition%20to%20the%20opposition%20Congress%20over%20the%20law-and-order%20situation%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaksha%20Khadse%2C%20Union%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Youth%20Affairs%20and%20Sports%20and%20a%20BJP%20leader%2C%20went%20to%20the%20police%20station%20today%20to%20file%20a%20complaint%2C%20accompanied%20by%20dozens%20of%20party%20workers%20and%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20yatra%20is%20organized%20every%20year%20in%20Kothali%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20Shivratri.%20My%20daughter%20went%20to%20this%20fair%20the%20day%20before%20yesterday%20and%20she%20was%20harassed%20by%20some%20boys.%20I%20have%20come%20to%20the%20police%20station%20to%20file%20a%20complaint%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20reporters%20outside%20the%20police%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20come%20as%20a%20mother%20seeking%20justice%2C%20not%20as%20a%20Union%20Minister%20and%20MP%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20a%20visibly%20upset%20Ms%20Khadse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKushanat%20Pingde%2C%20Deputy%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%2C%20Muktainagar%20said%20that%20the%20accused%20misbehaved%20with%20several%20girls%20and%20even%20clashed%20with%20their%20bodyguards%20when%20they%20tried%20to%20intervene.%20He%20has%20named%20seven%20accused%20in%20the%20case%2C%20of%20whom%20one%20has%20been%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDenying%20any%20political%20pressure%2C%20he%20said%20a%20case%20has%20been%20lodged%20for%20molestation%2C%20and%20under%20the%20POCSO%20Act.%20Charges%20under%20the%20IT%20Act%20have%20also%20been%20added%20since%20the%20accused%20also%20clicked%20the%20girls'%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%2C%20Ms%20Khadse%20-%20who%20belongs%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20that's%20in%20power%20in%20Maharashtra%20-%20raised%20a%20concern%20over%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20common%20people%20when%20even%20ministers'%20families%20are%20not%20safe.%20She%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20my%20own%20daughter%20is%20not%20safe%2C%20what%20will%20be%20the%20condition%20of%20others%3F%20I%20will%20demand%20strict%20action%20from%20the%20state%20government%20for%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20law.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20daughter%20of%20a%20public%20representative%20is%20being%20harassed%2C%20then%20what%20about%20the%20safety%20of%20common%20citizens%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20sought%20to%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Khadse%2C%20a%20three-time%20MP%20from%20the%20Raver%20seat%2C%20said%20crimes%20against%20women%20have%20increased%20across%20Maharashtra%20and%20there%20is%20no%20fear%20of%20law.%20Many%20girls%20hesitate%20to%20come%20forward%2C%20but%20we%20must%20not%20stay%20silent%2C%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20would%20meet%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20demand%20action%20on%20such%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Congress%20chief%20Harshwardhan%20Sapkal%20also%20sharpened%20his%20attack%20after%20the%20incident%20and%20demanded%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20to%20step%20down%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%20He%20also%20blamed%20the%20Mahayuti%20-%20the%20ruling%20coalition%20headed%20by%20BJP%20-%20and%20alleged%20that%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20had%20collapsed%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20has%20been%20a%20huge%20increase%20in%20atrocities%20against%20women%20and%20girls%20in%20the%20state%20due%20to%20the%20presence%20of%20goons.%20If%20the%20daughters%20of%20Union%20Ministers%20are%20not%20safe%2C%20it%20is%20better%20not%20to%20think%20about%20the%20condition%20of%20the%20children%20of%20the%20common%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20an%20online%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20situation%2C%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20said%20the%20workers%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bparticular%20party%26quot%3B%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20crime%20and%20that%20strictest%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20the%20crime%20involved%20workers%20from%20a%20particular%20party.%20Cops%20have%20registered%20a%20case%20and%20arrested%20some%20people.%20The%20rest%20will%20be%20arrested%20soon.%20Those%20involved%20will%20not%20be%20spared.%20Strictest%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20against%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Fadnavis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20coming%20on%20the%20heels%20on%20the%20Pune%20rape%20case%20has%20shaken%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20Tuesday%2C%C2%A0a%2026-year-old%20woman%20was%20raped%20inside%20an%20empty%20bus%20parked%20at%20the%20Swargate%20depot%20in%20Pune%20city.%20Following%20an%20extensive%20search%20operation%2C%20the%20cops%20arrested%20the%20accused%2C%C2%A0Dattatray%20Ramdas%20Gade%2C%20from%20a%20paddy%20field.%20Reports%20suggest%20the%20accused%20had%20earlier%20been%20arrested%20for%20robbery%2C%20but%20has%20been%20out%20on%20bail%20since%202019.%20He%20faces%20several%20cases%20of%C2%A0theft%2C%20robbery%2C%20and%20chain-snatching.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740909060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fqu4a7vjg_raksha-khadse-police-station_625x300_02_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdaughter-harassed-in-maharashtra-union-minister-raksha-khadse-asks-if-common-citizens-are-safe-7829355%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20junior%20minister%20in%20the%20Union%20cabinet%20has%20raised%20questions%20over%20women's%20safety%20in%20Maharashtra%20after%20her%20minor%20daughter%20was%20harassed%20at%20a%20fair%20in%20Jalgaon%20district%2C%20giving%20ammunition%20to%20the%20opposition%20Congress%20over%20the%20law-and-order%20situation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdaughter-harassed-in-maharashtra-union-minister-raksha-khadse-asks-if-common-citizens-are-safe-7829355%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%2C%20Out%2C%20In%2C%20Out%3A%20Mayawati's%20Nephew%20Loses%20Top%20Party%20Post%20In%20New%20Flip-Flop%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAkash%20Anand%2C%20the%20nephew%20of%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%20chief%20Mayawati%2C%20has%20been%20removed%20as%20the%20party's%20national%20coordinator%20for%20the%20second%20time%20in%20a%20year.%20Mayawati%20has%20replaced%20the%2030-year-old%20with%20two%20national%20coordinators%20--%20Akash's%20father%20Anand%20Kumar%20and%20senior%20party%20leader%20Ramji%20Gautam.%20A%20BSP%20release%20says%20Akash%20Anand%20has%20been%20removed%20from%20all%20party%20posts%2C%20raising%20questions%20about%20his%20political%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20decisions%20were%20taken%20at%20a%20grand%20BSP%20meeting%20in%20Lucknow%2C%20chaired%20by%20Mayawati%20and%20attended%20by%20party%20leaders%20from%20across%20the%20country.%20The%20meeting%20reviewed%20the%20strategy%20of%20BSP%2C%20which%20has%20been%20struggling%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20which%20it%20ruled%20in%20the%20past%2C%20and%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Chequered%20Journey%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkash%20Anand%2C%20who%20studied%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Noida%20before%20completing%20his%20MBA%20from%20the%20UK's%20University%20of%20Plymouth%2C%20was%20showcased%20as%20the%20BSP's%20future%20and%20Ms%20Mayawati's%20political%20heir.%20He%20first%20emerged%20on%20the%20political%20scene%20ahead%20of%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20Positioned%20as%20a%20new-age%20face%2C%20he%20is%20considered%20to%20have%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20pushing%20BSP's%20social%20media%20presence.%20Towards%20the%20end%20of%202023%2C%20he%20was%20appointed%20the%20party's%20national%20coordinator%2C%20officially%20establishing%20him%20as%20Number%202%20in%20BSP.%20However%2C%20shortly%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20last%20year%2C%20Mayawati%20removed%20him%20from%20the%20top%20post%2C%20saying%20he%20needed%20%26quot%3Bmaturity%26quot%3B.%20Akash's%20father%20replaced%20him.%20The%20BSP%20was%20routed%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20winning%20zero%20seats.%20Soon%20after%2C%20Akash%20Anand%20was%20reappointed%20as%20national%20coordinator%20in%20June.%20Now%2C%20eight%20months%20later%2C%20he%20is%20out%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Mayawati%20said%20she%20would%20name%20anyone%20her%20political%20heir%20and%20added%20that%20her%20family%20will%20not%20forge%20any%20ties%20with%20another%20political%20family%20in%20the%20future.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Build-Up%20And%20A%20Big%20Hint%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20clear%20indication%20of%20Akash%20Anand%20losing%20favour%20with%20the%20BSP%20chief%20came%20last%20month%20when%20his%20father-in-law%20Ashok%20Siddharth%20was%20expelled%20from%20the%20BSP%20for%20anti-party%20activities.%20In%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Ms%20Mayawati%20said%20former%20MP%20Siddharth%20and%20Nitin%20Singh%20had%20been%20expelled%20for%20factionalism%20and%20other%20anti-party%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDays%20later%2C%20the%20BSP%20chief%20dropped%20a%20big%20hint.%20She%20said%20in%20a%20long%20thread%20that%20as%20the%20political%20heir%20of%20BSP%20founder%20Kanshi%20Ram%2C%20she%20would%20struggle%20lifelong%20to%20free%20Dalits%20from%20political%20slavery%20and%20social%20helplessness.%20Without%20taking%20names%2C%20she%20added%20that%20her%20true%20heir%20could%20only%20be%20someone%20committed%20to%20taking%20the%20movement%20forward%20despite%20all%20odds.%20The%20remark%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20swipe%20to%20Akash%20Anand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Floundering%20Political%20Force%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BSP's%20leadership%20flip-flops%20are%20playing%20out%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20its%20massive%20electoral%20setbacks%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years%20that%20have%20raised%20questions%20about%20its%20political%20future.%20The%20BSP%2C%20which%20won%20206%20seats%20in%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Assembly%20in%202007%2C%20won%20just%20one%20seat%20in%20the%202022%20state%20polls.%20In%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20the%20party%20won%2010%20seats%20in%20the%202019%20polls%2C%20when%20it%20contested%20in%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party.%20This%20time%2C%20it%20decided%20to%20go%20solo%20and%20drew%20a%20blank%20and%20new%20political%20forces%20such%20as%20the%20Chandrashekar%20Azad-led%20Azad%20Samaj%20Party%20dented%20the%20BSP's%20traditional%20support%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740908940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fsef5k7h8_mayawati-with-nephew-and-political-heir-akash-anand-ians_625x300_08_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmayawati-akash-anand-in-out-in-out-mayawatis-nephew-loses-top-party-post-in-new-flip-flop-7829431%22%2C%22summary%22%3