ng%20West%20Bengal.%20We%20will%20respond%20strongly%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20evident%20how%20the%20BJP%20is%20tampering%20with%20the%20voters'%20list%20with%20the%20blessings%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission's%20statement%20did%20not%20mention%20Ms%20Banerjee%20and%20said%20that%20the%20poll%20body%20took%20note%20of%20social%20media%20posts%20and%20media%20reports%20flagging%20duplicate%20EPIC%20numbers%20of%20people%20from%20different%20states.%20%26quot%3BIn%20this%20regard%2C%20it%20is%20clarified%20that%20while%20EPIC%20numbers%20of%20some%20of%20the%20electors%20may%20be%20identical%2C%20the%20other%20details%20including%20demographic%20details%2C%20Assembly%20Constituency%20and%20polling%20booth%20are%20different%20for%20the%20electors%20with%20the%20same%20EPIC%20number.%20Irrespective%20of%20the%20EPIC%20number%2C%20any%20elector%20can%20cast%20a%20vote%20only%20at%20their%20designated%20polling%20station%20in%20their%20respective%20Constituency%20in%20their%20State%2FUT%20where%20they%20are%20enrolled%20in%20the%20electoral%20roll%20and%20nowhere%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20poll%20body%20explained%20that%20this%20duplication%20was%20due%20to%20a%20decentralised%20and%20manual%20mechanism%20followed%20before%20the%20shifting%20of%20states'%20electoral%20roll%20database%20to%20the%20ERONET%20platform.%20%26quot%3BThis%20resulted%20in%20certain%20State%2FUT%20CEO%20offices%20using%20the%20same%20EPIC%20alphanumeric%20series%20and%20leaving%20a%20scope%20for%20the%20possibility%20of%20duplicate%20EPIC%20numbers%20being%20allotted%20to%20electors%20in%20different%20Assembly%20Constituencies%20in%20different%20States%2FUTs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20to%20allay%20any%20apprehensions%2C%20the%20Commission%20has%20decided%20to%20ensure%20allotment%20of%20unique%20EPIC%20number%20to%20registered%20electors.%20A