r%2C%20latched%20on%20to%20the%20remarks%20and%20said%20they%20had%20debunked%20the%20Congress's%20propaganda%20against%20the%20LDF%20government.%20Chief%20Minister%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%20said%20Mr%20Tharoor's%20statements%20are%20based%20on%20facts.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20about%20Kerala%2C%20not%20about%20any%20political%20party%20or%20government.%20All%20Keralites%20should%20feel%20proud%20of%20our%20growth%20amidst%20heavy%20odds.%20There%20is%20no%20need%20to%20give%20any%20political%20colour%20to%20his%20words%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20Congress%20unit%20responded%20strongly%20and%20said%20Mr%20Tharoor%20should%20not%20betray%20the%20expectations%20of%20the%20thousands%20of%20party%20workers%20ahead%20of%20the%20local%20body%20polls.%20Veekshanam%20Daily%2C%20Congress's%20mouthpiece%20in%20Kerala%2C%20published%20an%20editorial%20that%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20had%20been%20opposing%20shortcomings%20of%20the%20LDF%20government%20inside%20and%20outside%20the%20Assembly%20and%20it%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bsuicidal%26quot%3B%20to%20weaken%20the%20party%20from%20within.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20this%20row%20could%20die%20down%2C%20another%20uproar%20erupted%20over%20Mr%20Tharoor's%20remarks%20in%20a%20Malayalam%20podcast%20with%20The%20Indian%20Express.%20His%20remarks%20on%20having%20multiple%20options%20to%20spend%20his%20time%20were%20misconstrued%20as%20a%20hint%20that%20he%20was%20exploring%20options%20politically.%20The%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20contested%20another%20remark%20attributed%20to%20him%2C%20decrying%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20leader%20In%20Kerala%20Congress.%20Mr%20Tharoor%20said%20he%20had%20made%20no%20such%20remark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20row%2C%20Kerala%20Congress%20chief%20K%20Sudhakaran%20said%20Mr%20Tharoor's%20statements%20were%20likely%20meant%20to%20strengthen%20the%20party.%20%26quot%3BAs%20KPCC%20president%2C%20I%20will%20do%20my%20best%20to%20address%20any%20concerns%20and%20bring%20necessary%20corrections%20to%20the%20party's%20functioning%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20asserting%20that%20he%20would%20stand%20by%20the%20senior%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20row%20formed%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20Kerala%20Congress%20strategy%20meeting%20in%20Delhi%20that%20was%20attended%20by%20party%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20and%20senior%20leaders%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20and%20KC%20Venugopal.%20Mr%20Sudhakaran%2C%20Congress%20Legislature%20Party%20leader%20in%20the%20Kerala%20Assembly%20V%20D%20Satheesan%2C%20Mr%20Tharoor%20and%20AICC%20in-charge%20of%20Kerala%20Deepa%20Dasmunshi%20were%20also%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20said%20at%20the%20meeting%20that%20leaders%20should%20be%20very%20careful%20about%20the%20political%20strategy%20and%20should%20not%20do%20or%20say%20anything%20that%20does%20not%20follow%20the%20party%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20meeting%2C%20Ms%20Dasmunshi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20got%20a%20clear%20indication%20from%20our%20high%20command%20that%20the%20Congress%20is%20very%20much%20connected%20with%20the%20people%20of%20Kerala%20emotionally%20and%20politically.%20People%20are%20looking%20for%20a%20change%2C%20so%20we%20should%20not%20do%20anything%20that%20will%20disrespect%20the%20people%20of%20Kerala.%20This%20was%20a%20clear%20indication%20and%20if%20anyone%20(says)%20anything%20personally%2C%20we%20will%20take%20strong%20action.%20Because%20we%20have%20no%20right%20to%20disrespect%20the%20people%20of%20Kerala.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20stressed%20that%20the%20party%20stands%20united.%20%26quot%3BThe%20media%20is%20giving%20a%20wrong%20impression%20that%20there%20is%20no%20unity%20in%20the%20Congress%20in%20Kerala%2C%20which%20is%20untrue.%20Everyone%20here%20has%20expressed%20strongly%20against%20the%20LDF%20and%20the%20BJP.%20The%20leaders%20are%20strongly%20united%20and%20they%20will%20speak%20in%20a%20univocal%20voice%