vating%20the%20SK-4%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20rhizomes%20or%20fingers%20are%20planted%20in%20nursery%20bags%20in%20April%2C%20and%20by%20June%20they%20are%20transplanted%20on%20fields%20prepared%20with%20organic%20fertiliser.%20In%20August%2C%20the%20saplings%20are%20fed%20a%20second%20dose%20of%20water-soluble%20fertiliser.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crop%20is%20irrigated%20till%20January%20and%20harvested%20in%20the%20last%20week%20of%20February%2C%20with%20each%20sapling%20yielding%203.2%20kg%20or%20more.%20He%20has%20been%20propagating%20the%20variety%20for%20ten%20years%20now%20and%20regularly%20imparts%C2%A0training%20on%20plantation%20management%20to%20farmers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGrowing%20the%20rhizomes%20in%20nursery%20bags%20rather%20than%20planting%20them%20directly%20on%20the%20field%20offers%2090%20per%20cent%20success%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20farmer%20Gajendra%20Paunikar%20(55)%20of%20Nigundan%20village%2C%20who%20was%2C%20till%20very%20recently%2C%20the%20Agriculture%20Extension%20Officer%2C%20Panchayat%20Samiti%2C%20Guhagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGrown%20in%2013%20states%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20NIF%20event%20held%20in%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Rashtrapati%20Bhavan%20farmers%20from%20Nandurbar%2C%20Vidarbha%20along%20with%20farmers%20from%2013%20states%20bought%20tubers%20of%20the%20SK-4%20variety%20for%20cultivation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Protection%20of%20Plant%20Varieties%20%26amp%3B%20Farmers%20Rights%20Authority%20(PPV%26amp%3BFRA)%20granted%20to%20SK-4%20last%20December%2C%20Kachekar%20has%20been%20recognised%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cplant%20breeder%E2%80%9D%20and%20has%20the%20exclusive%20right%20to%