0team%2C%20he%20mentions%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20set%20up%20solar%20pumps%20which%20fill%20up%20the%20water%20holes%20as%20well%20as%20provide%20water%20to%20the%20interior%20forest%20%3Cem%3Echowki%3C%2Fem%3Es.%20Earlier%2C%20our%20staff%20would%20find%20it%20difficult%20to%20stay%20in%20a%20remote%20%3Cem%3Echowki%20%3C%2Fem%3Eduring%20the%20dry%20season.%20Things%20have%20become%20much%20easier%20after%20solar%20pump%20installations.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLast%20year%2C%20we%20experienced%20a%20very%20dry%20summer%20with%20no%20winter%20rains%20at%20all.%20These%20water%20holes%20helped%20a%20lot%20in%20ensuring%20wildlife%20had%20at%20least%20a%20few%20points%20in%20the%20jungle%20where%20there%20would%20be%20water%20throughout%20the%20year.%20The%20water%20hole%20ideally%20needs%20to%20be%20filled%20up%20once%20a%20week%20and%20during%20hot%20summers%20once%20in%202-3%20days.%20We%20were%20earlier%20dependent%20on%20water%20tankers.%20On%20a%20rough%20estimate%2C%20we%20now%20save%20about%20Rs%2030%2C000%20per%20year%20for%20each%20water%20hole%20because%20of%20these%20solar-pump-based%20systems%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20help%20of%20CSR%20backing%20by%20corporations%20and%20funds%20raised%20by%20generous%20benefactors%2C%20the%20couple%20continues%20to%20carve%20the%20path%20forward.%20Dr%20Sarita%20mentions%20that%20it%20costs%20them%20Rs%205%20lakh%20to%20support%20a%20solar-powered%20water%20pump%20in%20a%20given%20forest%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20challenges%20of%20working%20in%20remote%20and%20often%20inaccessible%20areas%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20been%20tirelessly%20advocating%20for%20the%20seamless%20integration%20of%20clean%20energy%20and%20wildlife%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDFcLh-Jv2Me%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%